text: Ayoub El Harrak (born 28 January 1999) is a Belgian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for the Belgian club Eupen. ==Professional career== El Harrak made his professional debut with K.A.S. Eupen in a Belgian First Division A 3-1 loss to Beerschot on 19 May 2018. On 13 June 2019, El Harrak signed his first professional contract with Eupen. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:People from Fléron Category:Belgian footballers Category:Belgian people of Moroccan descent Category:K.A.S.
